text: (a) (a) National toll-Free number and other communication capabilities Section 1271(c) of the Public Health Service Act ( 42 U.S.C. 300d–71(c) ) is amended by striking fiscal years 2020 through 2024 and inserting fiscal years 2025 through 2029 ..
